event.logging

Interface EventAction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlertEventAction, ApprovalEventAction, AuthenticateEventAction, AuthoriseEventAction, BaseObjectOutcome, CopyEventAction, CreateEventAction, DeleteEventAction, ExportEventAction, ImportEventAction, InstallEventAction, MoveEventAction, NetworkEventAction, PrintEventAction, ProcessEventAction, ReceiveEventAction, SearchEventAction, SendEventAction, UninstallEventAction, UnknownEventAction, UpdateEventAction, ViewEventAction

    public interface EventAction
    Marker interface for all EventAction implementations. Describes the main action of an event, i.e. what happened. For example viewing a document or copying a file.
